nodes.text: Level 5121 was a level on the planet Coruscant. The Commission for a Safe and Secure Republic, a nonprofit think tank, was based on Level 5121. Sannab Ro, a Xidelphiad artist for the Commission, was in chrysalis on the level following the Hosnian Cataclysm, and was slated to re-emerge sometime in the next fifteen years as a male.
